<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.8.8">
<l>kuṭiyil piṟantavar ceyyuṅ kuṇamoṉ ṟuñceyti laṉantō</l>
<l>naṭaiyoṉṟuñ ceytilaṉ naṅkāy nantakō paṉmakaṉ kaṇṇa</l>
<l>ṉiṭaiyiru pālum vaṇaṅka viḷaittiḷait teṉmaka ḷeṅki</l>
<l>kaṭaikayi ṟēpaṟṟi vāṅkik kaitaḻum pēṟiṭuṅ kolō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Alas! He has not done one thing of quality,</l>
<l rend="indent">which are done by those born to [his] clan.</l>
<l>Ladies! Kaṇṇaṉ, Nandagōpa’s son</l>
<l rend="indent">has not done one thing [according to] custom.</l>
<l>Will my daughter, languishing, grow weaker and weaker</l>
<l rend="indent">so that both sides of her waist bend,</l>
<l>Becoming exhausted, grasping the churning rope,</l>
<l rend="indent">welts rising on her hands.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
